委任律師提起上訴者，應一併繳納上訴審裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　2 　　月　　11　　日\r\n                            書記官  陳柏志","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/STEV/110%2c%e5%ba%97%e5%b0%8f%2c1773%2c20220211%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"STEV,110,店小,1773,20220211,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"店小","JNO":"1773","JDATE":"20220211","JTITLE":"損害賠償"}